        "content": "<p>There is this small TODO in the file <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/11100128fea213a315f2b4a4bd98e9b8ff1b2057/Mathlib/Algebra/DirectSum/Basic.lean#L251-L255\">Algebra/DirectSum/Basic.lean</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- TODO: generalize this to remove the assumption `S ⊆ T`.</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">/-- `setToSet β S T h` is the natural homomorphism `⨁ (i : S), β i → ⨁ (i : T), β i`,</span>\n<span class=\"sd\">where `h : S ⊆ T`. -/</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setToSet</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⊆</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">toAddMonoid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">of</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Subtype</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨↑</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The following definition generalizes <code>setToSet</code> and it coincides with the original when <code>S ⊆ T</code> (under the hypothesis of <code>DecidablePred (· ∈ T)</code>). Is it PR worthy?</p>\n<p>There is an analogous one for a linear map in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/11100128fea213a315f2b4a4bd98e9b8ff1b2057/Mathlib/Algebra/DirectSum/Module.lean#L130\">Algebra/DirectSum/Module.lean</a> that can be extended in the same way.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">DirectSum</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AddCommMonoid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">DecidableEq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">/-- New definition: -/</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setToSetNew</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">DecidablePred</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⨁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">toAddMonoid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">then</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">of</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨↑</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setToSet_eq_setToSetNew_of_subset</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">DecidablePred</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⊆</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">setToSet</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setToSetNew</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">setToSet</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">setToSetNew</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">toAddMonoid_inj</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">ext</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">H</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
